name: Rogue Robot Games & Comics
directions: The restroom is shared by multiple businesses in that building, but the easiest way to get to it is to enter Rogue Robot and ask to use the bathroom. It's down a twisty back hallway.
comment:
You do not need to be a customer to use the bathroom. Rogue Robot is a very LGBTQ-friendly business. The bathrooms are spacious and employees try to keep them clean. 

Unfortunately not really accessible, as they are down an outdoor flight of about 6 stairs, BUT if you have someone with you who can go in OR a cell phone and you can call the store, the employee can meet you at the back door off Michigan Street and let you in. The door is at ground level and to use the bathroom you don't need to go down any stairs, but to enter the store there is one shallow approximately six-inch-drop stair.
